\section*{-Extravasation}

Due to drug leakage into tissues e.g. All Cytotoxics, Sulphur drugs, Potassium drugs ,bismuth drugs

Causes Inflammation, vesicles; Skin necrosis may occur within 24 hrs \& Gangrene secondary to vascular spasm in 2-3days.MxPrevention close monitoring, Iv line in forearm and flush line well.
