- Club feet
- Kyphoscoliosis
- Rib cage anomalies
C)Genitourinary
- Hydronephrosis
- Hydroureters
- Horse shoe kidneys
- Un-descended testis
D)Cardiopulmonary
- VSD,ASD
c)Gastrointestinal systems
- Malrotations
- Emphaloceles
